
Doc:
    Submission: Everything under one "lpjs submit" command
    Job: An independent computational run
	Serial
	Multithreaded
	MPI

Required submission parameters
    Jobs
    Cores per job
    Nodes per job
    
    Array: Jobs > 1
    Multithreaded: nodes per job = 1, cores per job = # or "all"
    MPI: Cores per job > 1

lpjs shell

lpjs cancel job|submission #

